After speaking with support there are a few ways we can reschedule this =
session.

You or I can join directly the session to reschedule the time by =
clicking on Menu > Reschedule Session.
=EF=BF=BC

Or I can reschedule the session directly.

=EF=BF=BC

The last option is terminating the session and for me to send you a =
booking link.

We can also leave this session open to when we need to next meet but =
there is a chance the session will time out and automatically close.

Have a Blessed Day

~Evan McCall


